TO WIND HIM UP.

27:12.892 --> 27:14.676
HE'S THE DIRECTOR.

27:14.676 --> 27:17.679
I'M SORRY. HE AMUSES ME.I'M GLAD HE ENTERTAINS YOU,

27:17.679 --> 27:20.290
