TOO MUCH.

27:22.510 --> 27:24.164
[speaks inaudibly]

27:24.164 --> 27:27.689
I'LL CATCH UP.

27:27.689 --> 27:32.302
[speaks indistinctly]

27:32.302 --> 27:33.695
EXCUSE ME?

27:33.695 --> 27:35.741
WHAT DID YOU TELL HER?

27:35.741 --> 27:37.743
I WAS COMPLIMENTING HER
ON HER JACKET.

27:37.743 --> 27:40.093
IT'S SUCH A VIVID COLOR.LIAR.

