ON THIS THING 24/7.

27:49.929 --> 27:53.628
I WANT TO EXTEND MY SYMPATHIES
TO THE FAMILY OF PETER RUSSO,

27:53.628 --> 27:55.978
AND--AND PLEASE JOIN US
IN OUR PRAYERS

27:55.978 --> 27:58.024
FOR MR. DUBLIN'S SAFETY.

27:58.024 --> 28:00.200
ARE THERE QUESTIONS--
BRIEFLY, PLEASE?

28:00.200 --> 28:03.377
