BEING A SEX-RELATED CRIME MAYBE?

28:03.377 --> 28:06.380
I MEAN, THAT ALLEYWAY IS--NO, THERE'S NO SEX ANGLE, JEFF--
NONE THAT WE'RE AWARE OF.

28:06.380 --> 28:09.731
SIR, DO YOU THINK THERE'S
A BRIXHAM LAKE CONNECTION HERE?

28:09.731 --> 28:13.300
NO. I DON'T THINK SO.BUT BOTH YOU AND DUBLIN ARE
INVOLVED IN THAT CASE,

28:13.300 --> 28:16.259
AREN'T YOU?NO, NO, NO.
WH-WHAT WE'RE THINKING IS,

28:16.259 --> 28:19.132
IT SEEMS
THAT MR. DUBLIN WAS RUMORED

28:19.132 --> 28:22.091
TO KEEP A LARGE DIAMOND
WITH HIM, ON--ON HIS PERSON,

28:22.091 --> 28:24.920
AND THE THEFT OF THAT DIAMOND IS
OUR CURRENT LINE OF THINKING

28:24.920 --> 28:26.443
AS TO MOTIVE.

