A DIAMOND LIKE THAT

28:33.407 --> 28:36.366
AROUND WITH HIM? WELL, THAT'S
A GOOD QUESTION, JEFF.

28:36.366 --> 28:38.717
UH, PERHAPS MR. DUBLIN
WAS TRYING TO BE PREPARED

28:38.717 --> 28:39.848
FOR ANY CIRCUMSTANCE.

28:39.848 --> 28:41.545
YOU KNOW...

28:41.545 --> 28:43.504
[turns TV on] ...UNDERSTANDABLE, ISN'T IT?

28:43.504 --> 28:46.246
I MEAN,
HE'S, UH, HAD A TOUGH...[clicks switch]

