GUESSING GAMES WITH ME?

29:20.497 --> 29:22.978
NO, IT'S JUST THAT
I'M NOT SURE MYSELF.

29:22.978 --> 29:25.372
I HAVE A PLAN, THOUGH.OH, SHEEPDIP.

