YOU ARE STILL TRYING TO
PUNISH ME FOR LYING TO YOU.

29:29.028 --> 29:31.073
WELL, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M SORRY. SORRY.

29:31.073 --> 29:33.684
YOU WANTED OFF THIS CASE.
YOU'RE OFF.

29:33.684 --> 29:35.686
YOU CAN TAKE A NAP
IN YOUR THINKING ROOM.

29:35.686 --> 29:38.037
WE'LL SOLVE THIS CASE
WITHOUT YOU, THE RIGHT WAY--

29:38.037 --> 29:40.604
WITH
GOOD, SOLID DETECTIVE WORK.

29:40.604 --> 29:43.782
SO I TAKE IT YOU DON'T WANT
TO HEAR MY PLAN?

29:43.782 --> 29:47.176
"NO, I DON'T WANT
TO HEAR YOUR PLAN."

29:47.176 --> 29:49.744
"SHEEPDIP YOUR PLAN."

29:56.751 --> 29:58.405
[speaks indistinctly]

29:58.405 --> 30:00.755
HI, LADIES.

30:00.755 --> 30:02.148
WE'RE LOOKING FOR SUGAR.

30:02.148 --> 30:04.280
NO SUGAR. JUST CANDY.

30:04.280 --> 30:05.629
YOU'RE NOT SUGAR?

30:05.629 --> 30:08.067
NO, MA'AM. EXCUSE ME.

30:08.067 --> 30:10.069
YEAH, WELL,
WE KINDA THINK YOU ARE.

30:10.069 --> 30:12.114
YEAH, WELL,
THINKING'S FREE, FLACO.

30:12.114 --> 30:14.116
YOU'RE GONNA NEED TO COME
WITH US, SUGAR.

30:14.116 --> 30:16.075
WHAT FOR?BECAUSE YOU SAW
WHAT HAPPENED

30:16.075 --> 30:18.120
IN THAT ALLEYWAY
OVER ON FREMONT.

30:18.120 --> 30:20.122
NAH, I WAS JUST PLAYING.
I DIDN'T SEE NOTHING.

30:20.122 --> 30:22.821
OKAY, STILL,
WE'D LIKE FOR YOU--HEY! [grunts]

30:22.821 --> 30:25.432
OH! [grunts]

30:25.432 --> 30:27.564
[grunts]

30:27.564 --> 30:30.089
AAH! AAH!

30:32.482 --> 30:34.528
[sighs] OKAY.

30:34.528 --> 30:36.182
[sniffles] OHH.

30:36.182 --> 30:37.574
HERE.

30:37.574 --> 30:39.489
[inhales sharply] OHH.

30:41.883 --> 30:44.581
OHH.

30:44.581 --> 30:46.540
[whispers] THANKS.

30:46.540 --> 30:48.411
NO PROBLEM.

30:51.371 --> 30:52.720
[sighs] OKAY.

30:52.720 --> 30:54.548
I'M AT THE BRIDGE.

30:54.548 --> 30:56.550
CIGARETTE BREAK.

30:56.550 --> 30:58.552
LIMO COMES IN OFF FREMONT.

30:58.552 --> 31:00.597
I'M ABOUT TO GO OVER AND TALK BUSINESS,

31:00.597 --> 31:03.557
ONLY THIS PICKUP TRUCK COMES IN BEHIND IT AND BLOCKS THE LIMO.

31:03.557 --> 31:06.690
I'M THINKING, UH-OH,
SO I-I GET UP OUT OF SIGHT.

31:06.690 --> 31:09.345
AND WHAT KIND OF TRUCK?

31:09.345 --> 31:11.608
IT WAS A TRUCK.

31:11.608 --> 31:15.569
UH, GREEN
OR... OR--OR BROWN OR BLUE.

31:15.569 --> 31:16.962
NOT--NOT RED.

31:16.962 --> 31:19.529
AND, UH,
A WHITE GUY GETS OUT

31:19.529 --> 31:21.357
AND--AND SAYS, "HEY."

31:21.357 --> 31:23.185
WHAT'D HE LOOK LIKE?

31:23.185 --> 31:25.622
A WHITE GUY.
HE HAD A-A BLACK HAT ON.

31:25.622 --> 31:27.842
A WHITE GUY IN A BLACK HAT?YEAH. YEAH, AND THEN HE--
HE WALKS UP TO THE LIMO.

31:27.842 --> 31:29.713
THE LIMO DRIVER GETS OUT.

31:29.713 --> 31:32.325
HE'S LIKE, "HEY, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOUDOING HERE?"

31:32.325 --> 31:34.544
BLACK HAT DON'T SAY NOTHING.

31:34.544 --> 31:36.546
HE JUST PULLS OUT A PIECE AND BOOM!

31:36.546 --> 31:38.722
SHOOTS THE DRIVER THREE TIMES
AND THEN HE WALKS

31:38.722 --> 31:40.681
OVER TO THE LIMO DOOR

31:40.681 --> 31:42.552
AND DRAGS OUT
THIS BIG FAT GUY.

31:42.552 --> 31:44.337
"GET OUT," HE SAYS.

31:44.337 --> 31:47.122
AND THEN HE--HE WALKS HIM
TO THE BACK OF THE TRUCK

31:47.122 --> 31:50.430
AND MAKES HIM CLIMB IN THE BACK,
AND THE FAT DUDE'S CALM.

31:50.430 --> 31:54.477
HE'S LIKE, "YOU KNOW,
OKAY, WE CAN NEGOTIATE."

31:54.477 --> 31:56.088
AND THEN BOOM!

31:56.088 --> 31:58.612
[panting] BLACK HAT JUST...
SHOOTS HIM IN THE HEAD.

31:58.612 --> 32:00.614
AND THEN HE--HE PUTS A TARP OVER HIM,

32:00.614 --> 32:03.617
AND THEN HE JUMPS BACK
INTO HIS CAR AND HE TAKES OFF,

32:03.617 --> 32:06.098
AND THAT'S ALL THAT HAPPENED. TH-THAT WAS IT.

32:06.098 --> 32:08.665
OKAY.

32:08.665 --> 32:11.451
DO YOU RECOGNIZE THIS GUY?

32:11.451 --> 32:13.453
YEAH.

32:13.453 --> 32:15.150
THAT'S THE--THE FAT DUDE.

32:15.150 --> 32:17.631
HE WAS DEAD, YOU THINK?

32:17.631 --> 32:19.415
YEAH, HE'S DEAD.

32:24.725 --> 32:27.597
[sniffles]
SO THIS IS ABOUT ICE?

32:27.597 --> 32:29.904
ICE? WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

32:29.904 --> 32:31.862
WELL, THE TV SAID
THAT THE--THE FAT DUDE

32:31.862 --> 32:35.562
HAD, LIKE,
A $10 MILLION DIAMOND.

32:35.562 --> 32:38.695
YEAH, IT'S A THEORY.

