UM... IT'S VERY LATE.

33:02.676 --> 33:05.026
MM. I W--I WOULDN'T
INTRUDE LIKE THIS, UH,

33:05.026 --> 33:07.028
ONLY WE HAVE
AN IMPORTANT LEAD

33:07.028 --> 33:08.987
PERHAPS NADINE
CAN HELP US WITH.

33:08.987 --> 33:10.640
OH.

33:10.640 --> 33:13.861
UM, YEAH, PLEASE,
OF COURSE. OKAY.

33:13.861 --> 33:15.384
THANK YOU.

33:18.431 --> 33:21.434
UM, NOW YOU TOLD ME
THAT YOU AND YOUR FATHER

33:21.434 --> 33:23.436
TALKED ABOUT EVERYTHING
TOGETHER, YEAH?

33:23.436 --> 33:26.569
YES.DID YOU EVER TALK
ABOUT HIS WORK?

33:26.569 --> 33:28.571
SOMETIMES. BUT HE NEVER
MENTIONED A DIAMOND,

33:28.571 --> 33:30.791
IF THAT'S WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

33:30.791 --> 33:33.402
THE--WH--DIAMOND?IT SAID ON THE NEWS

33:33.402 --> 33:36.362
THEY WERE LOOKING FOR A DIAMOND
MR. DUBLIN HAD WITH HIM.

33:36.362 --> 33:40.192
UH, YEAH, THAT'S--
THAT'S JUST ALL TALK.SEE? I TOLD YOU.

33:40.192 --> 33:43.978
I MEAN, THERE'S A DIAMOND
ALL RIGHT. SO I HEAR, ANYHOW.

33:43.978 --> 33:46.676
UH, DUBLIN KEEPS IT HIDDEN
IN HIS FALSE TOOTH APPARENTLY,

33:46.676 --> 33:48.678
BUT NOBODY KNEW ABOUT IT,
SO I CAN'T SEE

33:48.678 --> 33:50.680
HOW ANYBODY COULD'VE BEEN
GOING AFTER IT. NO.

33:50.680 --> 33:53.683
NO, I THINK THIS IS ALL
CONNECTED TO A COURT CASE.

33:53.683 --> 33:55.816
DID YOUR DAD EVER MENTION
BRIXHAM LAKE?

33:55.816 --> 33:58.123
NO.

33:58.123 --> 34:00.908
YOU SURE? BRIXHAM LAKE.

34:00.908 --> 34:03.171
THINK HARD.

34:04.738 --> 34:06.696
WHAT ABOUT GALE BERTRAM?

34:06.696 --> 34:08.568
NO.

34:08.568 --> 34:10.483
OH.

34:10.483 --> 34:13.094
WELL,
THAT'S DISAPPOINTING.

34:13.094 --> 34:14.574
I WAS SURE...

34:18.665 --> 34:21.581
OH, WELL. UH...

34:21.581 --> 34:24.497
CAN'T WIN 'EM ALL.
[chuckles]

34:24.497 --> 34:26.673
THAT'S IT?

34:26.673 --> 34:29.632
BELIEVE ME, UH, I KNOW
I-IT'S HARD TO DEAL WITH,

34:29.632 --> 34:32.244
BUT, UM...

34:32.244 --> 34:34.637
YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES
THE BAD GUYS JUST GET AWAY.

34:34.637 --> 34:38.685
BUT YOU SAID YOU'D CATCH THEM.
YOU GUARANTEED IT.

34:38.685 --> 34:41.601
[sighs]

34:43.603 --> 34:44.995
[sighs]

34:44.995 --> 34:46.736
[whispers indistinctly]

34:46.736 --> 34:50.131
[cell phone rings]

34:50.131 --> 34:53.178
[ring]

34:53.178 --> 34:56.659
[ring]

34:56.659 --> 34:58.531
[ring]

35:02.796 --> 35:05.799
HEY, LISBON.
HOW'S THE DETECTIVE WORK DOING?

35:05.799 --> 35:07.409
[Lisbon] EH, DOING OKAY.

35:07.409 --> 35:09.455
WELL, I TELL YOU WHAT.

35:09.455 --> 35:11.805
COME OVER AND MEET ME
AT NADINE RUSSO'S HOUSE,

35:11.805 --> 35:14.590
