SOMETHING EXCITING.

35:14.590 --> 35:16.418
LISBON?

35:16.418 --> 35:17.767
YOU THERE?

35:17.767 --> 35:19.421
LISBON?

35:19.421 --> 35:20.814
[loud tap][gasps]

35:20.814 --> 35:22.685
[shuts cell phone]

35:25.688 --> 35:27.342
HI.

35:27.342 --> 35:29.388
HI.

35:29.388 --> 35:31.259
