ABOUT SIX MONTHS AGO,

38:00.800 --> 38:02.889
NADINE WAS...

38:02.889 --> 38:05.761
STAYING OUT PAST CURFEW,

38:05.761 --> 38:09.417
DRINKING AND SMOKING--

38:09.417 --> 38:11.724
YOUR BASIC TEENAGE STUFF.

38:11.724 --> 38:13.769
[sighs]

38:13.769 --> 38:16.032
SO WE HAD
A BIG CONVERSATION

38:16.032 --> 38:17.686
ABOUT THE RULES,

38:17.686 --> 38:20.733
AND--AND THINGS GOT
