38:20.733 --> 38:22.735
YOU KNOW, AS THEY DO.

38:22.735 --> 38:24.127
YES.

38:24.127 --> 38:25.607
[sighs]

38:25.607 --> 38:28.610
LOOK, I FELT THAT
SHE WAS OVER-THE-LINE RUDE

38:28.610 --> 38:31.831
TO HER MOTHER AND ME,
