38:31.831 --> 38:35.791
I'M NOT PROUD OF IT.

38:35.791 --> 38:37.750
BUT I-IT WAS A TAP.

38:37.750 --> 38:39.142
REALLY.

38:39.142 --> 38:41.144
IT WAS NO BIG DEAL.

38:43.538 --> 38:46.759
ANYWAY, NADINE TOLD PETE
ABOUT IT.

38:46.759 --> 38:49.457
HE GOT MAD.

38:49.457 --> 38:51.633
[sighs]

38:51.633 --> 38:54.680
PETE AND I WERE BUDDIES.

38:54.680 --> 38:57.639
YOU KNOW, WE COULD'VE HAD
A BEER AND A DISCUSSION,

38:57.639 --> 39:01.426
AND WE COULD'VE
WORKED IT OUT.

39:01.426 --> 39:04.080
NO, BUT HE COMES
INTO MY HOUSE...

39:04.080 --> 39:08.084
[Keith] AND I DON'T EVEN HAVE A CHANCE TO DEFEND MYSELF!

39:08.084 --> 39:10.739
I MEAN,
HE SUCKER PUNCHES ME,

39:10.739 --> 39:13.829
