39:16.484 --> 39:18.660
AND MY STEPDAUGHTER.

39:18.660 --> 39:20.749
PUT HIS FOOT ON MY NECK,

39:20.749 --> 39:23.622
AND HE SPAT ON ME...

39:23.622 --> 39:25.885
IN MY OWN HOUSE!

39:25.885 --> 39:27.713
THAT'S NOT RIGHT.

39:27.713 --> 39:31.543
EVEN AFTERWARDS, I-IT'S LIKE
I'M THE ONE TO BLAME. NO.

39:31.543 --> 39:34.067
PATRICIA INSISTED
THAT WE MAKE PEACE

39:34.067 --> 39:35.808
FOR NADINE'S SAKE.

39:35.808 --> 39:39.638
HE DOES THAT TO ME, AND I'M
SUPPOSED TO JUST SWALLOW IT?

39:39.638 --> 39:41.814
NOBODY WOULD.

39:41.814 --> 39:45.774
OH, I THOUGHT ABOUT WAYS
TO PAY HIM BACK.

39:45.774 --> 39:47.863
OH, I THOUGHT
ABOUT IT A LOT.

39:47.863 --> 39:50.083
[inhales and exhales deeply]

39:50.083 --> 39:52.041
BUT I KNEW
THAT IF I KILLED HIM...

39:52.041 --> 39:53.695
[sighs]

39:53.695 --> 39:55.958
